name: OG Brainstorm Tee - Black
description: Circa 2007 around the time the Dead Fresh Crew was created the clothing line was called Brainstorm. Our slogan at the time, "Don't Just Think, Brainstorm." This design was our very first, it's a Thunder Cloud with a Cross-bone. The reason for the Dead Fresh Crew on the back was that the founders wanted exclusivity. Dead Fresh Crew distinguished their Brainstorm shirt from other Brainstorm shirts sold to friends. Soon people wanted Dead Fresh Crew on their apparel and now. "Right Your Own Destiny." p.s. Shoutout to printable cut out iron-ons from Costco.
